## Proposed Folder Structure

A production-ready, clean separation of concerns:

```text
src/
  ├── config/           # Database connection & configurations
  ├── controllers/      # Request/Response route controllers
  ├── middleware/       # Custom middleware (error handling, request validation)
  ├── models/           # Database models/queries (using SQL queries or Sequelize/Prisma)
  ├── routes/           # Express router endpoints
  ├── utils/            # Utilities (pagination, search-helpers, status codes)
  ├── app.js            # Express app initialization
  └── server.js         # Entry point to listen and run the server
package.json
.env                    # Environment variables (DB credentials, PORT)
```

