## Proposed REST API Endpoints

### 1. Students CRUD & Search (`/api/students`)
- `POST /api/students` - Create a student profile.
- `GET /api/students` - Retrieve students (supports pagination, filtering by `email` or `name`, and sorting).
- `GET /api/students/:id` - Retrieve a single student's profile.
- `PUT /api/students/:id` - Update student profile.
- `DELETE /api/students/:id` - Delete student (cascades and deletes enrollments).

### 2. Courses CRUD (`/api/courses`)
- `POST /api/courses` - Create a course.
- `GET /api/courses` - Retrieve all courses.
- `GET /api/courses/:id` - Retrieve a single course.
- `PUT /api/courses/:id` - Update course details.
- `DELETE /api/courses/:id` - Delete course (cascades and deletes enrollments).

### 3. Enrollments CRUD (`/api/enrollments`)
- `POST /api/enrollments` - Enroll a student in a course (body: `{ student_id, course_id }`).
- `GET /api/enrollments` - List all enrollments.
- `GET /api/students/:id/courses` - List courses a specific student is enrolled in.
- `GET /api/courses/:id/students` - List students enrolled in a specific course.
- `PUT /api/enrollments/:id` - Update enrollment grade.
- `DELETE /api/enrollments/:id` - Drop/unenroll a student from a course.

